{"tid":843500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不只退休！ 馬雲早已放棄阿里巴巴所有權","createTime":"2018-10-01T07:58:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T13:51:13.000Z","uid":184679,"like":270,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":120,"replies":[{"pid":"d1a63cd2517d69629feba2f2baad097de3cdfcf1","tid":843500,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:58:24.000Z","msg":"中國電商阿里巴巴創辦人馬雲在日前宣佈將退休後，阿里巴巴今（1）證實，馬雲已放棄阿里巴巴的所有權。<br />\n<br />\n《金融時報》報導，據阿里巴巴7月向美國證券交易委員會提交的文件，顯示馬雲已放棄阿里巴巴的所有權，將所有權轉交給5位新所有人，這5人的身份目前尚未披露。<br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴今也證實，創辦人馬雲已放棄對阿里巴巴主要「可變利益實體」的所有權。阿里巴巴屬於大多數中國在海外上市的「可變利益實體」公司之一，實體通常允許中國技術公司從海外實體獲得投資。<br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴稱，馬雲放棄所有權，是為了減輕行政負擔。<br />\n<br />\n馬雲則在9月10日宣佈，將在1年內卸任阿里巴巴執行董事長，將工作交給阿里巴巴集團執行長張勇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/2567064\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2567064&d=08CUcjX1i9ezszgZTk5EIEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=637066e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2567064&h=237e1a04\" target=\"_blank\">http://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/2567064</a>"},{"pid":"84b3cdc9b223d0f096da377683d11bc7918592b9","tid":843500,"uid":101110,"like":753,"dislike":3,"score":750,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T08:00:44.000Z","msg":"三十六計最後一計先係精華所在"},{"pid":"658815ce53b16e5a035f9a0a9b9c5436e53577b7","tid":843500,"uid":65371,"like":247,"dislike":3,"score":244,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T08:02:11.000Z","msg":"馬雲你走先，呢度我頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25de3669df2f5921a8ff59e36c77f08fea5005cb","tid":843500,"uid":165012,"like":351,"dislike":2,"score":349,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T08:02:31.000Z","msg":"之前又話唔係退落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n別讓馬雲跑了"},{"pid":"999bc4ada8e2509c75c961c708342695a05354be","tid":843500,"uid":23180,"like":403,"dislike":2,"score":401,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01